title: Mom Used Image Of Dead Daughter To Look Innocent.. | Big Boy's Neighborhood | KUBE 104.9
text:
Mom Used Image Of Dead Daughter To Look Innocent.. posted by Ani Caribbean - share 
Jeanie Ditty, a solider from Fort Bragg North Carolina, was arrested with her boyfriend, Zachary Keefer. They were both charged with first-degree murder, according to police. 
Sunny Jo, a photographer who created "ghost" photos, says he believes he was manipulated by the now! "She used my work to make people think that she's innocent, and that's so wrong," Jo said.
